components.templateData:
<mat-form-field [color]="color" class="example-chip-list">
    <mat-label>{{label}}</mat-label>
    <mat-chip-list #chipList aria-label="Chip selection">
        <mat-chip *ngFor="let chip of chips" [selectable]="selectable" [removable]="removable" (removed)="remove(chip)" [color]="chip.colorChip" [selected]="chip.selected">
            {{chip.name}}
            <mat-icon matChipRemove *ngIf="removable">{{icon}}</mat-icon>
        </mat-chip>
        <input [placeholder]="placeholder" [matChipInputFor]="chipList" [matChipInputSeparatorKeyCodes]="separatorKeysCodes" [matChipInputAddOnBlur]="addOnBlur" (matChipInputTokenEnd)="add($event)">
    </mat-chip-list>
</mat-form-field>

propertiesClass.name: range

components.templateData:
<ng-template [ngIf]="showRange">
    <mat-form-field [color]="color_input" appearance="fill" class="example-form-field">
        <mat-label>{{label}}</mat-label>
        <mat-date-range-input [formGroup]="range" [rangePicker]="rangePicker" [disabled]="completelyDisabled">
            <input matStartDate [placeholder]="placeholder_startDate">
            <input matEndDate [placeholder]="placeholder_endDate">
        </mat-date-range-input>
        <mat-datepicker-toggle matSuffix [for]="rangePicker" [disabled]="popupDisabled">
            <mat-icon matDatepickerToggleIcon>{{toggleIcon}}</mat-icon>
        </mat-datepicker-toggle>
        <mat-date-range-picker #rangePicker [color]="color_datepicker">
            <mat-date-range-picker-actions>
                <button mat-button matDateRangePickerCancel>{{label_cancelButton}}</button>
                <button mat-raised-button color="primary" matDateRangePickerApply>{{label_applyButton}}</button>
            </mat-date-range-picker-actions>
        </mat-date-range-picker>
        <mat-error *ngIf="range.controls.start.hasError('matStartDateInvalid')">Invalid start date</mat-error>
        <mat-error *ngIf="range.controls.end.hasError('matEndDateInvalid')">Invalid end date</mat-error>
    </mat-form-field>
</ng-template>

<ng-template [ngIf]="showRange == false">
    <mat-form-field class="example-full-width" appearance="fill">
        <mat-label>{{label}}</mat-label>
        <input matInput [matDatepicker]="picker">
        <mat-datepicker-toggle matSuffix [for]="picker">
            <mat-icon matDatepickerToggleIcon>{{toggleIcon}}</mat-icon>
        </mat-datepicker-toggle>
        <mat-datepicker #picker></mat-datepicker>
    </mat-form-field>
</ng-template>

components.name: SelectComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-form-field appearance="fill">
    <mat-label>{{label}}</mat-label>
    <ng-template [ngIf]="requiredSelection ==false">
        <mat-select>
            <mat-option *ngFor="let option of options" [value]="option.value">
                {{option.viewValue}}
            </mat-option>
        </mat-select>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template [ngIf]="requiredSelection">
        <mat-select matNativeControl required>
            <mat-option *ngFor="let option of options" [value]="option.value">{{option.viewValue}}</mat-option>
        </mat-select>
        <ng-template [ngIf]="showHint">
            <mat-hint>{{hint}}</mat-hint>
        </ng-template>
    </ng-template>
</mat-form-field>
